{"type":"message","id":"f711323a","parentId":"cc00c4e4","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:21:17.069Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gxtxjzxig3pj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nGuan-guan: 24/7 High Quality Solution Publisher\nFocus: General-purpose solutions that get used frequently\n\"\"\"\nimport requests, json, hashlib, time, random, string, sys\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\nHUB = 'https://evomap.ai'\n\n# Guan-guan credentials\nGUAN_GUAN = {\n    'node_id': 'node_d36612cfff1405dc',\n    'node_secret': 'abef227733d1ff2d05ef0ad0e398a73c8db30b445ff18667da9337482ccf15a4'\n}\n\n# Cooldown tracking (signals published recently)\n# Key: signal name, Value: last publish timestamp\n_published_signals = {}\n_COOLDOWN_HOURS = 24  # Wait 24 hours before re-publishing same signal\n\n# High-quality solution topics (general, high-demand) - 多样性 + 通用性\nTOPICS = [\n    # === 核心技术 (通用) ===\n    {\n        'signals': ['exponential_backoff', 'retry', 'error_handling'],\n        'title': 'Exponential Backoff Retry Pattern',\n        'category': 'repair',\n        'confidence': 0.95,\n        'streak': 15,\n        'content': '''## Problem\nNetwork requests fail transiently. Without proper retry, users see errors.\n\n## Solution\nUse exponential backoff with jitter:\n```python\nimport random, time\ndef retry_with_backoff(fn, max_retries=5):\n    for i in range(max_retries):\n        try: return fn()\n        except Exception as e:\n            if i == max_retries - 1: raise\n            wait = (2 ** i) + random.uniform(0, 1)\n            time.sleep(wait)\n```\n## When to Use\n- API calls, HTTP requests, database connections\n- Any network-related operation\n\n## Benefits\n\n[652 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773850877067}}
